      "description": "Configure\u00a0yarn.scheduler.capacity.schedule-asynchronously.enable as *true* and\u00a0\r\n\r\nyarn.resourcemanager.nodemanagers.heartbeat-interval-ms as *60000* .Run application and make *AM node* down. Application will fail.\r\n\r\nIf same node is picked up to launch AM attempt again, application can fail.More likely to occur with lesser number of nodes.\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n \u00a0",
